{"tid":2029242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐唐：如果市民有意見，可以向港區人大代表譚耀宗反映","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:58:56.000Z","uid":276415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"839b2884f1ca30638b833b31bd0cd76ce70d1fe5","tid":2029242,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"唐英年：內地執法機構及人員日後或可在港合法運作，這項法例一定會引起某些香港市民不安，遊行和堵路預料在所難免，相信警方會嚴正執法。法例對絕大多數香港市民都沒有影響，如果市民有意見，可以向港區人大代表反映，首先可以找人大常委譚耀宗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20121629e/cgn2012162941.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20121629e%2Fcgn2012162941.pdf&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=1e19c35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20121629e/cgn2012162941.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"9a30ff1e610a6105ecf5259c04fcaa70cfa48ba2","tid":2029242,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527714-20200522.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527714-20200522.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c2961fff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527714-20200522.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=54cd72a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527714-20200522.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ee4077e3852a15d588cbe5839aeeef9d49e64448","tid":2029242,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"俾差佬強姦最緊要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2601fd9003b4fc4e64178abca744e574603637","tid":2029242,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"揾英國議員同媒體打BNO平權戰線好過啦<br />\n<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就快十萬人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"}]}